<div id="tokenModal" class="modal fade" tabindex="-1" role="dialog" aria-hidden="true">
  <div class="modal-dialog">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <h5 class="modal-title">Hold on, citizen!</h5>
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="modal" aria-label="Close">
          <span aria-hidden="true">&times;</span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <p>In order to accept your input, cookies are used to keep track of your submissions on the website.</p>

        <p><a class="text-underline" href="{{ path('security_login') }}">Sign in or create an account</a> for an even better experience. How is it better? Shut up citizen and join the crew of No Agenda producers.</p>

        <p class="d-none text-danger" data-token-error>Failed to generate a cookie. Sorry about that.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-footer">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-secondary" data-dismiss="modal">Cancel</button>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" data-token-submit>Accept cookies</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
